Install this package by:

$ cd /path/to/repo.git
$ python setup.py install

To get data (warning, this takes a long time):

>> from friday_harbor.data.regenerate_data import regenerate_data
>> regenerate_data('/existing/path/to/data')

To use the library once you have the data downloaded:

>> from friday_harbor.experiment import ExperimentManager
>> experiment_manager = ExperimentManager()
>> for experiment in experiment_manager:
>>     ...

Dependencies (python packages):
	numpy/scipy
	h5py
	requests